-- U.S. Fed approves merger request of two Texas banks
-- By Emily Stephenson
-- Wed May 14, 2014 04:30PM EDT
-- None



WASHINGTON, May 14 (Reuters) - The U.S. Federal Reserve said on Wednesday it had approved a merger request from Texas-based financial firms Cullen/Frost Bankers <CFR.N> and WNB Bancshares.

